{"word":"Holy Spirit","slug":"holy-spirit","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Holy Spirit</b> - (Select Readings,)<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=14&verse=16'>Joh 14:16-26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=1'>Act 2:1-47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=1'>Rom 8:1-39</a><p/>(For alphabetical arrangement See Index)<p/><b>(1) General Work</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=4&verse=6'>Zec 4:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=28'>Mat 12:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=15&verse=26'>Joh 15:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=16&verse=8'>Joh 16:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=11'>Rom 8:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=26'>Rom 8:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=3&verse=6'>2Co 3:6</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=3&verse=18'>1Pe 3:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=1&verse=21'>2Pe 1:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=22&verse=17'>Rev 22:17</a><p/><b>(2) Dwelling in Believers</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=36&verse=27'>Eze 36:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=14&verse=17'>Joh 14:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=9'>Rom 8:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=3&verse=16'>1Co 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=6&verse=19'>1Co 6:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=1&verse=14'>2Ti 1:14</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=2&verse=27'>1Jo 2:27</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Spirit Filled, FULNESS<p/>Spiritu